ExternalData.EIF: provisionally on 26 January 1994, in accordance with article 8(1) and definitively on 25 March 1994, in accordance with article 8(1) of the Protocol and was terminated in accordance with its provisions on 1 January 2006, upon the entry into force of the International Agreement on Olive Oil and Table Olives, 2005, which is deposited with the Government of Spain..
